{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_50071.jpg","bgm":"bgm23_tokime04","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102601}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"The Daybreak Ceremony...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Sunao","textLeft":"It was plotted by Mikoshiba's ancestors...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"I verified with Lord Kyūbē, so I'm certain."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"To think they've been summoning danger@just to quell it, "},{"chara":[{"id":102601}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"all to boost their own authority..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"She tricked a Diviner into letting her use@her wish for her personal gain... "},{"chara":[{"id":102701,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"It is a despicable thing to do in any era..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Yes... It's very despicable and cowardly."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102501,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Hence why I want to end the ritual. "},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"I want to destroy the Calamity-Calling Cup@and overcome this evil practice,"},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"because I think that's what Miss Hatsu@wanted to accomplish."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"As do I...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"Me too!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102601,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"But how do we break the cup?"},{"chara":[{"id":102601,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"Can we use force, like hitting it?"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"According to legend,"},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"the cup is indestructible, hence@the ritual to appease it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"Is it true?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"It's likely the case..."},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"If it were destructible, Miss Hatsu would have@done so without needing to make a wish."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"Yeah, you're definitely right..."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Then we will have to use the sword@that Miss Hatsu wished for."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"They weakened its power so it could be@used in the ceremony, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102501,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Yes, the sword as it is now lacks@the brilliance it had in my dream..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"What did Mikoshiba do to it...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"Is there any way to fix it?"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"If we can return the part to@its rightful place,"},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"my understanding is that the sword@will regain its original power..."},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"But I have no clue where the missing@part went."},{"chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Lord Kyūbē doesn't know, either."},{"chara":[{"id":102601,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Chiharu","textRight":"Oh no..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"...But I won't give up!"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"id":102501}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"I think I will go to Kamihama City."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":400,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102601,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameCenter":"Sunao & Chiharu","textCenter":"[chara:102701:effect_emotion_surprise_0][chara:102601:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Huh?!"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
